OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FGoing to a football stadium to
OL,7,Finterview a club's new manager is
OL,8,Fsomething I have been fortunate enough
OL,9,Fto do a number of times.
OL,11,FRarely do they feel any different. You
OL,12,Fsee the same faces, you often hear the
OL,13,Fsame questions asked and you're
OL,14,Fregularly in a room full of the same
OL,15,Fjournalists.
OL,17,FThis time at Bristol City though
OL,18,Fdidn't feel the same.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FWe're more than a week on from Michael
OL,7,FSkubala joining the club. There was no
OL,8,Fpress conference. Instead, there were
OL,9,F1-1 sessions with the media - a better
OL,10,Fopportunity for all journalists to
OL,11,Fproperly meet the man who has been
OL,12,Ftasked with leading Bristol City into
OL,13,Fwhat he has called 'a new era'.
OL,15,FIt wasn't just him either. We were
OL,16,Fgiven allotted time to speak with the
OL,17,Fclub's Sporting Director too, James
OL,18,FEllis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FEllis has only been in the role for a
OL,7,Ffew weeks himself, the first sporting
OL,8,Fdirector City have ever had, but there
OL,9,Fhas been no easing-in period.
OL,11,FThere will no doubt be a number of
OL,12,Fjobs on his list. Top though would
OL,13,Fhave been appointing his first
OL,14,Fmanager, the face of what feels like a
OL,15,Fnew-look Bristol City.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FA bit of insight for fans - both men
OL,7,Fcome across very open and honest.
OL,8,FNeither carry the baggage that seems
OL,9,Fto come when you have worked in a
OL,10,Ffootball club for an extended period
OL,11,Fof time.
OL,13,FThere are a number of key phrases and
OL,14,Fwords they use.
OL,16,FBehaviours, Aligned, Elite and
OL,17,FTogetherness
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FIt's clear what the message is to
OL,7,Fsupporters. A new sporting Director, a
OL,8,Fnew Chief Executive in Charlie Boss,
OL,9,Fand a new manager. This club are
OL,10,Ffinally looking at a different way of
OL,11,Fgetting to the Premier League.
OL,13,FWhat are the challenges?
OL,15,FThis season will not be
OL,16,Fstraightforward though. The
OL,17,FChampionship is arguably the most
OL,18,Fcompetitive it has ever been.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FThere seems to be more clubs with
OL,7,Fparachute payments than ever before.
OL,8,FHuge Premier League clubs like Wolves,
OL,9,FBurnley and of course West Ham stand
OL,10,Fin their way.
OL,12,FThat is without mentioning those
OL,13,Falready in the division with bigger
OL,14,Fbudgets that the Robins.
OL,16,FAnother key issue both Skubala and
OL,17,FEllis will need to tackle is the
OL,18,Fcontract situation of a number of key
OL,19,Fplayers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FSome players are currently out of
OL,7,Fcontract but next summer will be a big
OL,8,Fproblem.
OL,10,FCaptain Jason Knight, Max Bird and
OL,11,FRoss McCrorie's deals all run out at
OL,12,Fthe end of next season. In theory, it
OL,13,Fmeans at that point if no extension is
OL,14,Fagreed they can walk away for nothing.
OL,16,FThe club was in a similar situation at
OL,17,Fthe turn of this year. It arguably
OL,18,Fderailed their season with top stars
OL,19,FAnis Mehmeti and Zak Vyner leaving to
OL,20,Fthen promotion rivals Ipswich and
OL,21,FWrexham respectively.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FEllis and the new manager will need to
OL,7,Fsell their Bristol City vision to
OL,8,Fthose players, convincing them to re-
OL,9,Fsign and commit to the "journey".
OL,11,FWhen I quizzed them on budget for the
OL,12,Fnext season, Ellis told me there would
OL,13,Fbe "investment".
OL,15,FThis club will certainly need that if
OL,16,Fits dreams of getting to the top
OL,17,Fflight are to be achieved. One thing
OL,18,Fin their favour though, the extended
OL,19,Fplay-offs providing more teams with a
OL,20,Fshot at the Premier League.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FWhat have they said?
OL,8,FSpeaking to me, Skubala said he is
OL,9,Fexcited to lead "a new era" for
OL,10,FBristol City. He wants togetherness
OL,11,Fand called for the backing of fans
OL,13,F"It is an amazing opportunity,"
OL,14,FSkubala said.
OL,16,F"When you look at the club in its
OL,17,Fhistory and the rich history it has
OL,18,Fhere, the amazing fanbase it has here,
OL,19,FI look at the end of last season and
OL,20,Fthe amount of fans they were still
OL,21,Fgetting, it is obvious why.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,F"There are players here with a desire
OL,7,Fto win.
OL,9,F"Some people think that you can't get
OL,10,FBristol to the Premier League. Why not?
OL,12,F"So that's why I'm here, to drive this
OL,13,Fclub into into a new era."
OL,15,FThat positivity is a non-negotiable
OL,16,Ffor anyone taking on role of manager
OL,17,Fbut Skubala comes from success.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FHis background includes huge promotion
OL,7,Fsuccess against the odds with Lincoln
OL,8,FCity last season. But it does go
OL,9,Fdeeper than that.
OL,11,FHe spent a long period with Leeds
OL,12,FUnited, but looking further back he
OL,13,Falso spent time at the elite centre of
OL,14,Fexcellence at Loughborough University.
OL,16,FHe has the ability to steadily build
OL,17,Fprogress. That is something Ellis also
OL,18,Fbrings given his won experience
OL,19,Fworking in top jobs at Premier League
OL,20,Fgiants Arsenal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FBoth men obviously praised the
OL,7,FLansdown family, who in recent months
OL,8,Fhave come under intense scrutiny.
OL,10,FIt came to a head on multiple
OL,11,Foccasions last campaign with some
OL,12,Fsections of the fanbase calling for
OL,13,FSteve Lansdown to sell the club.
OL,15,FThere has been interest over recent
OL,16,Fyears, most notably when Saudi Arabian
OL,17,Fbusinessman Turki Alalshikh visited
OL,18,Fthe training ground and stadium.
OL,20,FHe did then rule himself out but
OL,21,Frumours have swirled since.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FSpeaking to Ellis though, there seems
OL,7,Fto be very little sign of that
OL,8,Fhappening any time soon. Instead, the
OL,9,Fappointments and noise around the club
OL,10,Fseem to be gearing up for their
OL,11,Fbiggest assault on promotion for a
OL,12,Fnumber of years.
OL,14,FThe next few weeks' activity in the
OL,15,Ftransfer window will also be another
OL,16,Fbig indicator on that ambition.
OL,18,FWhat happens now?
OL,20,FThe timing of this appointment seems
OL,21,Freasonably good.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FThe club have acted to get the people
OL,7,Fin the right place before the transfer
OL,8,Fwindow starts and long before the
OL,9,Fstart of pre-season (staff and the
OL,10,Fplayers are back at the end of this
OL,11,Fmonth).
OL,13,FFans are entitled to feel it could
OL,14,Fhave been done sooner, with Gerhard
OL,15,FStruber sacked in March and Roy
OL,16,FHodgson only appointed on an interim
OL,17,Fbasis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781527685
OL,3,CMichael Skubala: 'Why can't Bristol
OL,4,CCity get to the Premier League'
OL,6,FEllis though would have been key to
OL,7,Fappointing a new manager or head coach
OL,8,Fand he has only been officially in the
OL,9,Fbuilding for a couple of weeks himself.
OL,11,FThe next few weeks are huge for
OL,12,FSkubala, Ellis and everyone at the
OL,13,Fclub. The squad will take shape, fans
OL,14,Fwill hear more from their new leaders
OL,15,Fand the picture of how the season
OL,16,Fcould look will become clearer.
OL,18,FThe vibe though is positive and fans
OL,19,Fshould feel that way as we hurtle
OL,20,Ftowards the start of the 2026-2027
OL,21,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
